WEBVTT

00:01.168 --> 00:02.334
I KNOW I WANT YOU.
WELL, THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

00:02.370 --> 00:03.635
WANT TO COME IN?

00:03.671 --> 00:06.739
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i> "IF LOVING YOU IS WRONG"...</i>

00:06.774 --> 00:09.241
-SHE LET HIM IN?
-Yeah.

00:09.276 --> 00:10.442
THIS DAMN SLUT.

00:10.478 --> 00:11.643
Stick to the plan.
Wait for him to come out.

00:11.679 --> 00:13.479
WE'RE GONNA CAVE
HIS PRETTY FACE IN.

00:13.514 --> 00:15.347
SHE SNAPPED AND SHE SHOT
HIS ASS AND THE ONE --

00:15.383 --> 00:16.882
ONE GOOD LAWYER
THAT'S IN THIS TOWN

00:16.917 --> 00:19.084
THAT OWES ME ALL THESE FAVORS
WON'T EVEN REP HER.

00:19.120 --> 00:20.252
I CAN'T.

00:20.287 --> 00:21.120
GOOD NIGHT.

00:21.155 --> 00:23.856
NIGHT.
THANK YOU.

00:23.891 --> 00:27.593
♪♪

00:27.628 --> 00:29.161
[ ALL GRUNTING ]

00:29.196 --> 00:31.130
NO!

00:31.165 --> 00:33.499
[ GRUNTING CONTINUES ]

00:33.534 --> 00:42.307
♪♪

00:42.343 --> 00:44.042
[ PANTING ]

00:44.078 --> 00:46.412
[ GRUNTS ]

00:46.447 --> 00:49.181
♪♪

00:49.216 --> 00:52.084
[ PANTING ]

00:53.654 --> 00:55.454
AAH!

00:55.489 --> 00:58.957
STEVEN!
STEVEN, WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:58.993 --> 01:00.826
OH, MY GOD!
STEVEN, STOP!

01:00.861 --> 01:02.528
WHAT'S GOING ON?
IT'S THAT DAMN EDDIE!

01:02.563 --> 01:04.363
OKAY, CALM DOWN.
IS HE HERE?

01:04.398 --> 01:05.697
NO, BUT I KNOW
HE'S BEHIND THIS.

01:05.733 --> 01:06.932
LET'S CALL THE STATION.
NO!

01:06.967 --> 01:08.000
I DO NOT
NEED THEIR BACKUP.

01:08.035 --> 01:09.668
STEVEN, CALM DOWN!
GO IN THE HOUSE!

01:09.703 --> 01:11.904
GO IN THE HOUSE,
ESPERANZA.

01:12.239 --> 01:15.607
[ CAR DOORS CLOSING ]

01:15.643 --> 01:18.911
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

01:18.946 --> 01:25.818
♪♪

01:25.853 --> 01:29.655
[ Ringing ]

01:29.690 --> 01:35.561
♪♪

01:35.596 --> 01:39.164
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

01:39.200 --> 01:44.736
♪♪

01:44.772 --> 01:45.938
HEY.

01:45.973 --> 01:47.372
HELLO? HEY.
NATALIE, LISTEN.

01:47.408 --> 01:49.408
I-- IS LUSHION THERE?
I NEED TO TALK TO HIM.

01:49.443 --> 01:51.109
WELL,
HELLO TO YOU, TOO.

01:51.145 --> 01:52.711
NAT, I'M SORRY
BUT THIS IS AN EMERGENCY.

01:52.746 --> 01:54.313
CAN YOU PLEASE PUT HIM
ON THE PHONE?

01:54.348 --> 01:58.383
LOOK, I'M GETTING TIRED OF ALL
Y'ALL CALLING HERE FOR MY MAN.

01:58.419 --> 01:59.818
I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

01:59.854 --> 02:02.221
I'M JUST KIDDING WITH YOU.
LUSHION!

02:02.256 --> 02:03.889
Lushion: YEAH?

02:03.924 --> 02:05.824
BUT I'M NOT KIDDING.
REALLY.

02:05.860 --> 02:08.193
-Sorry.
-LUSHION?

02:08.229 --> 02:10.429
HERE,
IT'S ESPERANZA.

02:10.464 --> 02:11.997
WHAT'S GOING ON?

02:12.032 --> 02:14.533
I DON'T KNOW.

02:14.568 --> 02:15.767
HEY.

02:15.803 --> 02:18.370
LUSHION, LISTEN, OKAY?
STEVEN WAS JUST AT MY HOUSE.

02:18.405 --> 02:19.805
OH, LOOK.
ESPERANZA.

02:19.840 --> 02:21.240
I know.
Just listen.

02:21.275 --> 02:24.276
HE WAS AT MY HOUSE
AND THEN THESE FOUR GUYS CAME,

02:24.311 --> 02:25.944
AND THEY GOT
INTO A FIGHT AND --

02:25.980 --> 02:27.613
ARE THEY --
ARE THEY ALL RIGHT?

02:27.648 --> 02:30.315
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

02:30.351 --> 02:32.618
STEVEN IS A BAD BOY.

02:32.653 --> 02:34.620
YEAH, THEY RAN.
I KNOW THAT.

02:34.655 --> 02:37.022
YEAH, LIKE I SAID,
STEVE IS A BAD BOY.

02:37.057 --> 02:38.524
Listen.

02:38.559 --> 02:41.159
STEVEN THINKS
THAT EDDIE SENT THEM.

02:41.195 --> 02:42.194
OH.

02:42.229 --> 02:43.996
THEN STEVEN MUST KNOW
HE DID THAT.

02:44.031 --> 02:45.531
Yeah, I know that.

02:45.566 --> 02:46.632
BUT I DON'T -- I DON'T LIKE
THE WAY HE LEFT HERE, OKAY?

02:46.667 --> 02:47.799
HE WAS VERY ANGRY.

02:47.835 --> 02:49.635
I'VE NEVER SEEN HIM
LIKE THAT BEFORE.

02:49.670 --> 02:50.769
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

02:50.804 --> 02:52.671
LUSHION, HE LEFT HERE
TO GO GET EDDIE.

02:52.706 --> 02:56.041
HE WENT TO THE PUB
TO GO FIND EDDIE.

02:56.076 --> 02:58.710
ALL RIGHT, I'M STILL
WAITING FOR THE PROBLEM.

02:58.746 --> 03:01.013
LUSHION,
HE IS MAD AS HELL.

03:01.048 --> 03:02.881
I've never seen him
like that before.

03:02.917 --> 03:03.916
THEN EDDIE SHOULD HIDE.

03:03.951 --> 03:04.983
Listen, Lushion.

03:05.019 --> 03:07.719
YOU HAVE TO GO TO THE PUB, OKAY?
PLEASE.

03:07.755 --> 03:09.988
I DON'T LIKE THE WAY
THIS IS LOOKING.

03:10.024 --> 03:11.423
LOOK, ESPERANZA.

03:11.458 --> 03:13.859
I -- I THINK
SOMEBODY'S GONNA GET HURT.

03:13.894 --> 03:15.060
ALL RIGHT, YEAH.

03:15.095 --> 03:17.195
THEN YOU AND STEVEN
SHOULDN'T GO THERE.

03:17.231 --> 03:19.631
ARE YOU GONNA GO OR NOT,
LUSHION?

03:19.667 --> 03:21.867
LOOK, THERE'S A LOT
OF POLICE IN THERE.

03:21.902 --> 03:23.435
HE'LL BE FINE.

03:23.470 --> 03:24.836
[ SIGHS ]
LUSHION, LISTEN TO ME.

03:24.872 --> 03:27.172
I HAVE NEVER SEEN STEVEN
SO ANGRY BEFORE.

03:27.207 --> 03:28.607
CAN YOU PLEASE JUST GO?

03:28.642 --> 03:30.108
LOOK, THE ONLY THING
YOU KNOW ABOUT STEVEN

03:30.144 --> 03:32.511
IS THAT HE WEARS
PURPLE DRAWERS, OKAY?

03:32.546 --> 03:34.246
So, please,
you do know less.

03:34.281 --> 03:35.647
YOU KNOW WHAT?
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

03:35.683 --> 03:37.349
THAT'S NOT FAIR FOR YOU
TO SAY TO ME RIGHT NOW.

03:37.384 --> 03:38.717
PLEASE, I'M ASKING YOU
FOR A FAVOR.

03:38.752 --> 03:39.851
CAN YOU GO?

03:41.422 --> 03:42.854
[ SIGHS ] ALL RIGHT,
YOU KNOW WHAT?

03:42.890 --> 03:44.456
I -- I -- OKAY.

03:44.491 --> 03:46.825
That's uncalled for.
I'm sorry.

03:46.860 --> 03:48.860
[ SIGHS ]
SO ARE YOU GONNA GO?

03:48.896 --> 03:50.395
LET ME TALK TO NATALIE.

03:50.431 --> 03:52.230
All right.

03:52.266 --> 03:53.498
ALL RIGHT.

03:55.202 --> 03:58.937
ALL RIGHT, HOLD ON.

03:58.973 --> 04:02.074
HERE YOU GO.
ALL RIGHT. WELL, JUST GO.

04:02.109 --> 04:06.511
NATALIE?
HELLO?

04:06.547 --> 04:08.847
[ SIGHS ]

04:08.882 --> 04:10.148
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

04:10.184 --> 04:12.317
♪♪

04:12.353 --> 04:14.186
YOU KNOW WHAT?
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

04:14.221 --> 04:16.955
WHY -- WHY ARE YOU
TAKING YOUR TIME?

04:16.991 --> 04:20.092
I JUST, UH, REALIZED...

04:22.596 --> 04:25.464
SHOULD GAVE STEVEN JUST
A LITTLE MORE TIME

04:25.499 --> 04:29.401
SO HE CAN WHOOP
EDDIE'S ASS, SO.

04:29.436 --> 04:31.970
[ BOTH LAUGH LIGHTLY ]

04:32.006 --> 04:33.605
YOU WRONG FOR THAT.
NO, NO, NO.

04:33.641 --> 04:38.310
THERE'S NO NEED TO RUSH.
HE GONNA BE JUST FINE.

04:39.780 --> 04:41.179
WHAT ARE YOU SITTING HERE
LOOKING AT ME FOR?

04:41.215 --> 04:44.516
ALL RIGHT.

04:44.551 --> 04:47.552
WOULDN'T MIND EDDIE HAVING
AN ASS-WHOOPING, EITHER.

04:47.588 --> 04:48.987
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:49.023 --> 04:50.722
THAT'S WHY I LOVE YOU.

04:52.526 --> 04:53.825
YOU UNDERSTAND ME.

04:53.861 --> 04:55.794
MM-HMM.

04:55.829 --> 04:58.797
-- Captions by VITAC --
www.vitac.com

04:58.832 --> 05:01.800
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

05:01.835 --> 05:04.970
♪♪

05:06.582 --> 05:09.349
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

05:09.384 --> 05:12.919
[ MUSIC PLAYING INDISTINCTLY
IN BACKGROUND ]

05:12.955 --> 05:22.229
♪♪

05:22.264 --> 05:23.530
THE HELL HAPPENED TO YOU?

05:23.565 --> 05:27.767
YOU DIDN'T TELL US
THAT BASTARD KNEW KARATE.

05:27.803 --> 05:30.470
ALL OF YOU COULDN'T
HANDLE THAT PUNK?

05:30.506 --> 05:32.305
NO.

05:34.443 --> 05:36.643
YOU KNOW
WHAT WE GOT TO DO NOW?

05:36.678 --> 05:38.378
KAL WENT TO THE HOSPITAL
AND GOT STITCHES.

05:38.413 --> 05:40.647
AND HE DAMN NEAR
BROKE MY LEG.

05:40.682 --> 05:43.450
[ SCOFFS LIGHTLY ]

05:43.485 --> 05:45.418
NEVER SEND A GROUP OF LADIES
TO DO A MAN'S JOB.

05:45.454 --> 05:47.654
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU IDIOTS
COULDN'T HANDLE THIS.

05:47.689 --> 05:49.890
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

05:49.925 --> 05:54.027
♪♪

05:54.062 --> 05:55.462
HEY, LADY.

05:55.497 --> 05:58.532
SO YOU SENT THEM.

05:58.567 --> 06:00.333
SENT WHO?

06:00.369 --> 06:03.537
I RECOGNIZE...

06:03.572 --> 06:05.438
MIGHT WANT TO GO JOIN
YOUR OTHER BOY IN THE HOSPITAL.

06:05.474 --> 06:06.973
HEY, I JUST HAD
A BRAWL IN HERE.

06:07.009 --> 06:08.842
WE AIN'T GONNA DO THIS
NO MORE.

06:08.877 --> 06:11.311
NO.
THIS AIN'T GONNA BE A BRAWL.

06:11.346 --> 06:12.546
IT'S OKAY.

06:12.581 --> 06:14.681
NO, IT AIN'T.

06:14.716 --> 06:17.017
THIS IS GONNA BE
AN ASS-KICKING.

06:17.052 --> 06:18.885
STEVEN --
AND IF ANY OF YOU

06:18.921 --> 06:21.288
EVEN<i> THINK</i>
ABOUT STEPPING IN,

06:21.323 --> 06:24.257
I WILL KILL YOU!

06:24.293 --> 06:26.026
STEVEN, I KNOW
YOU'RE ALL FIRED UP, MAN.

06:26.061 --> 06:28.428
I DIDN'T SEND ANYBODY
TO YOUR HOUSE.

06:28.463 --> 06:30.096
JUST BRING IT DOWN A NOTCH,
SIT DOWN,

06:30.132 --> 06:31.431
AND HAVE A BEER
WITH ME.

06:31.466 --> 06:35.168
[ GRUNTING ]

06:35.204 --> 06:42.108
♪♪

06:42.144 --> 06:44.844
[ SHOUTING, GRUNTING ]

06:44.880 --> 06:51.785
♪♪

06:51.820 --> 06:55.855
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

06:55.891 --> 06:57.958
Eddie: [ COUGHING ]

06:57.993 --> 07:01.628
♪♪

07:01.663 --> 07:04.831
[ BLOWS CONTINUE LANDING ]

07:04.866 --> 07:06.132
HEY, STEVEN!

07:06.168 --> 07:07.534
HEY, STEVEN, STEVEN, STEVEN.

07:07.569 --> 07:08.635
ENOUGH, ENOUGH, ENOUGH.

07:08.670 --> 07:11.438
YOU SEND
ANYONE ELSE AFTER ME!

07:11.473 --> 07:13.840
YOU ALL RIGHT?

07:13.875 --> 07:15.208
LEAVE ME ALONE.

07:15.244 --> 07:17.677
MOVE!

07:17.713 --> 07:19.512
I TOLD YOU
TO LEAVE HIM ALONE.

07:19.548 --> 07:20.814
YOU'RE OUT
OF YOUR LEAGUE.

07:20.849 --> 07:22.849
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST LET THIS GO?

07:22.884 --> 07:24.251
YEAH.

07:24.286 --> 07:27.020
I'M EDDIE, LOU-LOU.
I LET NOTHING GO.

07:27.055 --> 07:29.589
AND THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT WE'RE
GONNA PUT ON YOUR TOMBSTONE.

07:29.625 --> 07:32.826
"HERE LIES EDDIE,
WHO WOULDN'T LET IT GO."

07:32.861 --> 07:35.762
HEY, LUSHION.
WHO'S GONNA PAY FOR THIS MESS?

07:35.797 --> 07:37.130
WHAT YOU NEED TO DO
IS HELP YOUR BOY.

07:37.165 --> 07:39.666
I'M PRETTY SURE
HE GOT IT.

07:39.701 --> 07:42.202
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:42.237 --> 07:48.275
♪♪

07:48.310 --> 07:49.909
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

07:49.945 --> 07:52.846
♪♪

07:52.881 --> 07:54.547
[ COUGHS ]

07:54.583 --> 07:57.250
YO, GET THAT BLOW.
I NEED IT NOW.

07:57.286 --> 08:04.190
♪♪

08:04.226 --> 08:11.131
♪♪

08:11.166 --> 08:17.570
♪♪

08:17.606 --> 08:19.572
YOU'RE HERE LATE.
OH.

08:19.608 --> 08:22.809
HEY.

08:22.844 --> 08:24.377
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE STILL HERE.

08:24.413 --> 08:27.113
YEAH.
I GOT A LITTLE TIED UP.

08:27.149 --> 08:28.682
HAD SOME
CATCHING UP TO DO.

08:28.717 --> 08:31.251
OH, OKAY.

08:31.286 --> 08:33.853
WHAT YOU WORKING ON?

08:33.889 --> 08:34.921
UM, WELL, I --

08:34.956 --> 08:37.157
IS THAT
THE TRAVIS CAIN FILE?

08:38.660 --> 08:42.062
YEAH.

08:42.097 --> 08:44.798
I THOUGHT I TOLD YOU
TO GET RID OF THAT.

08:46.301 --> 08:49.402
YEAH, WELL, I WANTED TO
TALK TO YOU ABOUT THAT.

08:49.438 --> 08:52.839
THERE'S NOTHING TO TALK ABOUT.
GIVE THE FILE, MAN.

08:52.874 --> 08:55.208
YOU WANT SOMETHING DONE,
YOU GOT TO DO IT YOURSELF.

08:55.243 --> 08:57.010
JUST HOLD ON A MINUTE.

08:57.045 --> 08:59.379
GIVE ME THE FILE, IAN.

08:59.414 --> 09:02.716
SO YOU MEAN TO TELL ME,
AFTER EVERYTHING THIS KID'S DONE

09:02.751 --> 09:04.818
TO HER WE'RE JUST --
JUST GONNA BURY IT?

09:04.853 --> 09:08.154
GIVE ME
THE DAMN FILE, IAN.

09:08.190 --> 09:09.889
JUST -- JUST WAIT A MINUTE,
OKAY?

09:09.925 --> 09:10.890
WAIT?

09:10.926 --> 09:12.025
LET'S TALK ABOUT THIS.
YEAH.

09:12.060 --> 09:14.694
WE REPRESENT HIS PARENTS
AND THEIR CHURCH --

09:14.730 --> 09:16.863
THE TUNE
OF MILLIONS OF DOLLARS.

09:16.898 --> 09:18.431
THERE IS NOTHING
TO WAIT FOR.

09:18.467 --> 09:19.766
GIVE ME THE FILE.
COME ON, LARRY.

09:19.801 --> 09:23.803
I THINK WE SHOULD
RECONSIDER THIS ONE.

09:23.839 --> 09:27.140
YOU HAVE AN OBLIGATION
TO YOUR CLIENT.

09:27.175 --> 09:29.075
HE'S NOT<i> MY</i> CLIENT.

09:30.545 --> 09:31.711
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING, IAN?

09:31.747 --> 09:33.546
I'M SAYING
HE'S<i> YOUR</i> CLIENT.

09:33.582 --> 09:35.014
MM-HMM.

09:35.050 --> 09:37.751
IAN, YOU WORK
FOR THIS FIRM, OKAY?

09:37.786 --> 09:39.552
AND SO DO I.

09:39.588 --> 09:42.555
THERE IS A CLEAR CONFLICT
OF INTEREST HERE.

09:44.926 --> 09:46.092
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

09:46.128 --> 09:48.061
MOST OF THE SHIT WE DO HERE
AIN'T RIGHT.

09:48.096 --> 09:49.462
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT, MAN?

09:49.498 --> 09:51.431
MAN, LARRY,
THIS ONE, THOUGH --

09:51.466 --> 09:53.400
ARE YOU
CHALLENGING ME, IAN?

09:53.435 --> 09:56.436
[ SIGHS ]
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

09:56.471 --> 09:59.239
WE ARE DEFENSE ATTORNEYS.

09:59.274 --> 10:02.175
SINCE WHEN DO WE GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT RIGHT OR WRONG?

10:02.210 --> 10:05.078
OR THE LAW,
FOR THAT MATTER?

10:05.113 --> 10:06.045
LOOK, SHE TRIED
TO COMMIT SUICIDE.

10:06.081 --> 10:06.913
WHO?

10:06.948 --> 10:08.148
HER -- KELLY ISSACS!

10:08.183 --> 10:09.849
AND?
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "AND?"

10:09.885 --> 10:12.318
AND IT'S BECAUSE OF EVERYTHING
THIS KID'S DONE TO HER.

10:12.354 --> 10:16.256
UH-HUH. AND THAT IS SUPPOSED
TO MATTER TO BE BECAUSE, WHY?

10:16.291 --> 10:18.625
HMM.
WAIT A SECOND.

10:18.660 --> 10:20.693
ARE YOU SLEEPING
WITH HER?

10:20.729 --> 10:21.828
OF COURSE NOT.

10:21.863 --> 10:23.530
ARE YOU SURE?

10:23.565 --> 10:24.798
DON'T YOU DARE.
NO, NO, NO, NO.

10:24.833 --> 10:26.733
MAYBE THAT EXPLAINS
WHY YOU WOULD FEEL THE NEED

10:26.768 --> 10:28.268
TO COME INTO THIS OFFICE

10:28.303 --> 10:29.769
AND TAKE PAPERWORK
THAT WOULD EXONERATE HER.

10:29.805 --> 10:32.472
IS THAT IT?
YOU KNOW THAT'S NOT IT.

10:32.507 --> 10:33.673
OKAY.

10:33.708 --> 10:37.710
SO MAYBE I SHOULD JUST TURN YOU
OVER TO THE BAR.

10:37.746 --> 10:40.079
YOU KNOW DAMN WELL
I GOT SO MUCH ON YOU.

10:40.115 --> 10:42.182
OH, YEAH.
I'M SURE YOU DO.

10:42.217 --> 10:44.684
BUT YOU DON'T PLAY BONDAGE
WITH SEVERAL MEMBERS

10:44.719 --> 10:47.487
OF THE BAR ASSOCIATION,
DO YOU?

10:47.522 --> 10:49.355
OR DO YOU?

10:49.391 --> 10:51.357
YOU'RE RIDICULOUS,
LARRY.

10:51.393 --> 10:53.426
[ CHUCKLES ] I'MMA TELL YOU
THIS ONE MORE TIME.

10:53.462 --> 10:56.496
GIVE ME THE FILE
OR WHEN I WALK OUT THIS DOOR,

10:56.531 --> 10:57.764
SO DOES YOUR CAREER.

10:57.799 --> 11:00.066
[ SIGHS ]

11:03.572 --> 11:06.339
WHATEVER, LARRY.

11:06.374 --> 11:08.107
GOOD BOY.

11:08.143 --> 11:13.513
NOW, IF THERE'S AN E-MAIL CHAIN,
A COPY, TAPE RECORDING,

11:13.548 --> 11:14.848
A PIECE OF STRING
THAT IS TIED TO YOUR FINGER

11:14.883 --> 11:16.349
TO HELP YOU REMEMBER
ANY OF THIS,

11:16.384 --> 11:19.018
I STRONGLY RECOMMEND
YOU GET RID OF IT ALL.

11:19.054 --> 11:22.622
OR, I'LL EAT YOUR ASS
FOR BREAKFAST.

11:22.657 --> 11:24.891
YOU KNOW ME.

11:24.926 --> 11:26.359
GOOD NIGHT, PARTNER.

11:26.394 --> 11:28.761
YOU'RE A WEIRD DUDE,
LARRY.

11:28.797 --> 11:30.563
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

11:31.666 --> 11:34.133
[ SIGHS ]

11:36.738 --> 11:41.140
♪♪

11:41.176 --> 11:42.942
NURSE?

11:42.978 --> 11:47.447
♪♪

11:47.482 --> 11:50.116
GIRL, WHY DO YOU KEEP
CALLING ME? YOU CAN'T SLEEP?

11:50.151 --> 11:52.051
NO!
I'M SURE.

11:52.087 --> 11:54.087
CAN YOU JUST
LOOSEN THESE?

11:54.122 --> 11:56.089
NO, I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

11:56.124 --> 11:57.223
PLEASE?

11:57.259 --> 11:58.992
HONEY,
YOU ARE A PRISONER.

11:59.027 --> 12:01.094
YOU HAVE TO BE HANDCUFFED
TO THE BED.

12:01.129 --> 12:02.762
WE DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU GONNA DO AROUND HERE,

12:02.797 --> 12:04.163
KILLING THAT MAN
AND A LOT OF THAT.

12:04.199 --> 12:06.232
OH, MY GOD.
I CANNOT BELIEVE THIS.

12:06.268 --> 12:07.867
WELL,
YOU BETTER BELIEVE IT.

12:07.903 --> 12:08.935
AND YOU BETTER
TOUGHEN UP.

12:08.970 --> 12:11.404
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU GOING?

12:12.741 --> 12:15.942
THEY AIN'T GONNA LOOSEN IT,
SO YOU MAY AS WELL STOP ASKING.

12:15.977 --> 12:17.076
I WASN'T TALKING TO YOU!

12:17.112 --> 12:19.879
WELL,
I'M TALKING TO YOU.

12:19.915 --> 12:21.047
NURSE?

12:21.082 --> 12:22.482
THEY DON'T CARE.
NURSE!

12:22.517 --> 12:24.284
THEY DON'T CARE.

12:24.319 --> 12:27.320
YOU THINK YOU ONE OF THEM
'CAUSE YOU BETTER THAN ME?

12:27.355 --> 12:30.223
WHY DON'T YOU SHUT THE HELL UP
AND MIND YOUR DAMN BUSINESS?

12:30.258 --> 12:31.991
OKAY.

12:32.027 --> 12:34.060
BUT YOU KNOW
THEY GONNA GET YOU, RIGHT?

12:34.095 --> 12:36.663
THEY GONNA KILL YOU.

12:36.698 --> 12:38.331
BUT I DON'T BLAME YOU,
THOUGH.

12:38.366 --> 12:40.934
I WOULD'VE TRIED TO TAKE THE
OPTIONS OUT OF THEIR HANDS, TOO,

12:40.969 --> 12:42.268
'CAUSE IT SHOULD BE
YOUR CHOICE.

12:42.304 --> 12:44.070
WHY DON'T YOU
SHUT THE HELL UP?

12:44.105 --> 12:45.471
BITCH, KEEP TALKING TO ME
LIKE THAT.

12:45.507 --> 12:47.373
-YOU KNOW --
-THAT'S IT, CARLY.

12:47.409 --> 12:48.641
THERE IS NOTHING
WRONG WITH YOU.

12:48.677 --> 12:49.943
Y'ALL TAKE HER
BACK TO HER CELL!

12:49.978 --> 12:51.210
COME ON, MAN.
MY BACK!

12:51.246 --> 12:54.247
YOU'RE FINE.
NOW GO. GO.

12:55.550 --> 12:57.417
HI.
KELLY, RIGHT?

12:57.452 --> 12:59.686
MY NAME IS MARGARET.
I'M THE CHAPLAIN HERE.

12:59.721 --> 13:02.322
WOULD YOU LIKE PRAYER?

13:02.357 --> 13:03.523
NO.

13:03.558 --> 13:05.959
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT WE ALL FORGIVE YOU.

13:08.163 --> 13:09.929
WHO IS "WE"?

13:09.965 --> 13:12.765
ALL OF US
AT THE CALVARY CHURCH.

13:12.801 --> 13:14.100
WHAT?

13:14.135 --> 13:16.069
TRAVIS' CHURCH.

13:16.104 --> 13:18.071
HE WAS A GOOD MAN.

13:18.106 --> 13:19.772
NURSE?
NO, I'M NOT HERE TO HARM YOU.

13:19.808 --> 13:22.375
NURSE!
I ONLY WANT TO PRAY FOR YOU.

13:22.410 --> 13:24.344
YOU SHOULD'VE BEEN
PRAYING FOR HIM.

13:24.379 --> 13:26.312
I DO.
I PRAY FOR HIS SOUL.

13:26.348 --> 13:28.214
NO, NO, YOU SHOULD'VE BEEN
PRAYING FOR HIM

13:28.249 --> 13:29.882
BEFORE HE DID WHAT HE DID!

13:29.918 --> 13:33.987
YOU KNOW LYING IS A SIN.

13:34.022 --> 13:35.288
I'M NOT LYING.

13:35.323 --> 13:37.757
WELL.

13:37.792 --> 13:40.927
ARE YOU A TRUE WOMAN
OF GOD?

13:40.962 --> 13:42.462
YES, I AM.

13:42.497 --> 13:46.532
THEN WHY DON'T YOU PRAY THAT GOD
WILL REVEAL THE TRUTH TO YOU?

13:46.568 --> 13:48.034
I ALREADY KNOW THE TRUTH.

13:48.069 --> 13:49.502
OH, YEAH?
AND WHAT'S THAT?

13:49.537 --> 13:52.905
THAT YOU STALKED HIM
UNTIL YOU KILLED HIM.

13:52.941 --> 13:54.674
BUT YOU KNOW,
GOD FORGIVES.

13:54.709 --> 13:58.344
THAT IS NOT THE TRUTH, BECAUSE
THAT'S WHAT HE DID TO ME.

13:58.380 --> 14:01.581
I WAS TOLD THAT
YOU WOULD SAY THAT TO ME.

14:01.616 --> 14:03.449
TOLD BY WHO?
HIS PARENTS.

14:03.485 --> 14:05.818
YOU'RE NOT THE FIRST WOMAN
TO SAY THAT.

14:07.722 --> 14:09.822
WAIT.
WAIT, WHAT?

14:09.858 --> 14:12.625
NO, NO, NO.
THEY -- THEY ALL GET JEALOUS.

14:12.661 --> 14:15.595
HIS FATHER'S PROMINENT
AND POWERFUL.

14:15.630 --> 14:18.598
HOW MANY?
HOW MANY WHAT?

14:18.633 --> 14:22.368
HOW MANY WOMEN SAID THAT?

14:22.404 --> 14:24.504
YOU DID.

14:24.539 --> 14:25.872
NO.

14:25.907 --> 14:28.474
YOU JUST SAID
THAT THERE WERE OTHER WOMEN.

14:28.510 --> 14:30.109
OH, YES.
BUT WE'RE TALKING ABOUT YOU.

14:30.145 --> 14:32.478
NO.

14:32.514 --> 14:34.180
NO.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

14:34.215 --> 14:37.350
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA TALK TO ME
ABOUT TRUTH,

14:37.385 --> 14:41.087
AND ABOUT FOR TRUTH AND
FOR WHAT THUS SAYETH THE LORD...

14:41.122 --> 14:42.355
MS. KELLY

14:42.390 --> 14:44.023
...SOME TRUST IN HORSES
AND SOME TRUST IN CHARIOTS,

14:44.059 --> 14:45.825
BUT I WILL TRUST
IN THE NAME OF THE LORD.

14:45.860 --> 14:46.926
OH, YOU KNOW THAT BIBLE.

14:46.961 --> 14:48.227
FOR THE NAME OF THE LORD
IS A STRONG TOWER.

14:48.263 --> 14:49.328
OH.

14:49.364 --> 14:50.363
THE RIGHTEOUS RUN THERE
AND THEN BE SAFE.

14:50.398 --> 14:51.364
YOU KNOW THAT ONE, TOO.

14:51.399 --> 14:52.365
THOU PREPAREST A TABLE
BEFORE ME

14:52.400 --> 14:53.566
IN THE PRESENCE
OF MINE ENEMIES.

14:53.601 --> 14:54.567
WELL THEN, HERE'S ONE
THAT YOU SHOULD KNOW!

14:54.602 --> 14:56.602
THOU ANOITEST
MY HEAD WITH OIL.

14:56.638 --> 14:58.037
THOU SHALT NOT KILL!

14:58.073 --> 15:02.542
♪♪

15:02.577 --> 15:10.316
IF YOU CALL YOURSELF A WOMAN
OF GOD, AND YOU SAY YOU PRAY,

15:10.351 --> 15:14.954
PLEASE ASK GOD
TO REVEAL THE TRUTH TO YOU.

15:14.989 --> 15:15.988
HE ALREADY HAS.

15:16.024 --> 15:17.690
THE VERY TRUTH.

15:17.726 --> 15:19.726
OH.
JUST, PLEASE.

15:19.761 --> 15:21.527
JUST ASK HIM.

15:23.198 --> 15:24.430
OKAY.

15:24.466 --> 15:27.033
I WILL.

15:27.068 --> 15:29.602
GOOD.

15:29.637 --> 15:31.204
NOW LEAVE.

15:31.239 --> 15:33.940
OKAY.

15:33.975 --> 15:35.742
GOD BLESS YOU.

15:35.777 --> 15:38.044
AND GOD BLESS YOU.

15:38.847 --> 15:41.414
NURSE?

15:41.449 --> 15:43.282
NURSE?

15:43.318 --> 15:46.919
NURSE!

15:46.955 --> 15:48.221
GOOD LORD, WHAT IS IT?

15:48.256 --> 15:50.089
I'M HAVING CHEST PAINS.

