KELLY, ALL OF YOUR VITALS
ARE NORMAL.

15:56.831 --> 16:00.233
I'M HAVING CHEST PAINS!

16:00.268 --> 16:01.934
SO NOW I GOTTA DO SOME PAPERWORK
TO SEND YOUR ASS

16:01.970 --> 16:03.369
TO THE HOSPITAL.
THAT'S RIGHT.

