UH, OKAY.

21:25.276 --> 21:27.209
WELL, YOU PROBABLY
SHOULDN'T TAKE THAT

21:27.245 --> 21:28.277
'CAUSE YOU CAN
GET ADDICTED TO IT

21:28.312 --> 21:29.512
IF YOU'RE
A RECOVERING ADDICT.

21:29.547 --> 21:32.047
WHO SAID ANYTHING
ABOUT RECOVERING, HUH?

21:32.083 --> 21:33.916
I SAID
I<i> AM</i> AND ADDICT.

21:33.951 --> 21:35.618
SO THIS BULLSHIT AIN'T GONNA
DO NOTHING FOR MY PAIN.

21:35.653 --> 21:39.054
I NEED SOMETHING
MUCH STRONGER.

21:39.090 --> 21:42.925
OFFICER WILLIS, DO YOU KNOW
THAT I CAN REPORT YOU?

21:45.196 --> 21:47.029
YOU KNOW I CAN REPORT YOU?

21:47.064 --> 21:48.430
FOR WHAT?

21:48.466 --> 21:50.032
WHEN YOU JUST GAVE ME
THAT PROSTATE EXAM,

21:50.067 --> 21:52.434
YOU KEPT YOUR FINGER UP THERE
FOR QUITE SOME TIME, DOC.

21:52.470 --> 21:55.371
I NEVER GAVE YOU
A PROSTATE EXAM.

21:55.406 --> 21:57.973
AIN'T GONNA BE
MY STORY.

21:58.009 --> 22:03.846
♪♪

22:03.881 --> 22:05.781
YOU KNOW WHAT?

22:07.919 --> 22:12.188
YOU'RE AN UNETHICAL,
HORRIBLE PERSON.

22:13.491 --> 22:15.457
WHAT I NEED YOU TO DO IS WRITE
ABOUT TWO OR THREE OF THEM, DOC,

22:15.493 --> 22:18.027
AND I'LL FIGURE OUT
WHAT I NEED MY DAMN SELF.

22:19.096 --> 22:22.898
EXACTLY WHAT I THOUGHT.
GET TO IT.

22:22.934 --> 22:25.201
AND ANOTHER ONE.

22:25.236 --> 22:34.476
♪♪

22:34.512 --> 22:36.178
GIVE YOUR PEN.

22:36.214 --> 22:38.647
SAY SOMETHING.

22:40.952 --> 22:43.285
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT IT IS.

22:43.321 --> 22:46.021
IT'S LIKE IT JUST KEEPS BEATING
REALLY FAST.

22:46.057 --> 22:48.090
IT JUST, LIKE --
IT JUST FEELS LIKE THE RHYTHM

22:48.125 --> 22:50.459
IS KIND OF OFF, YOU KNOW?

22:50.494 --> 22:51.894
IT'S LIKE --

22:51.929 --> 22:53.596
MMM, MMM, MMM.

22:54.999 --> 22:56.465
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

22:56.500 --> 22:58.100
GET AWAY FROM ME.

22:58.135 --> 22:59.602
WHAT'S GOING ON WITH HER,
NURSE?

22:59.637 --> 23:01.804
I CANNOT TELL YOU THAT.

23:05.877 --> 23:07.042
WELL,
HOW YOU FEELING, KELLY?

23:07.078 --> 23:08.777
I SAID, LEAVE ME ALONE.

23:08.813 --> 23:13.849
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU FEELING,
BUT YOU LOOK LIKE HELL.

23:13.885 --> 23:16.619
YEAH?
WELL, SO DO YOU.

23:16.654 --> 23:19.355
LOOK AT YOU -- WENT AND BOUGHT
A HOUSE FOR A MAN,

23:19.390 --> 23:21.824
THEN KILLED TWO OF THEM.

23:21.859 --> 23:23.492
EDDIE.

23:23.527 --> 23:25.194
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY'RE
CALLING YOU OUT HERE?

23:25.229 --> 23:28.397
THEY'RE CALLING YOU
THE BLACK WIDOW.

23:28.432 --> 23:30.432
YOU GET IT?

23:30.468 --> 23:33.002
BLACK...

23:33.037 --> 23:34.670
WIDOW.

23:34.705 --> 23:36.105
AND NOW YOU'RE SITTING HERE
CHAINED UP

23:36.140 --> 23:39.375
LIKE SOME KIND OF
A FARM ANIMAL IN THIS CHAIR.

23:40.578 --> 23:41.810
[ SCOFFS ]

23:41.846 --> 23:43.012
YOU KNOW WHAT KIND OF ANIMAL
I THINK YOU LOOK LIKE?

23:43.047 --> 23:45.981
WHY DON'T YOU SAY IT
SO I CAN CUSS YOUR ASS OUT.

23:46.017 --> 23:47.750
I THINK YOU LOOK LIKE
A BIG-ASS MULE

23:47.785 --> 23:50.319
THAT'S BEEN RIDDEN
INTO THE GROUND.

23:50.354 --> 23:52.454
GO TO HELL.

23:52.490 --> 23:55.090
WHAT DID YOU THINK
I WAS GONNA SAY, HUH?

23:55.126 --> 23:57.026
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN.

23:57.061 --> 24:00.429
'CAUSE I WOULD NEVER SAY
ANYTHING RACIST.

24:00.464 --> 24:01.797
NURSE?
OH, YEAH.

24:01.832 --> 24:02.831
GO AHEAD, SCREAM.
NURSE?

24:02.867 --> 24:04.700
NO, SCREAM LOUDER.

24:04.735 --> 24:06.702
SEE THIS LITTLE JEWELRY
THEY GOT YOU IN?

24:06.737 --> 24:10.839
MEANS YOU GET NO RESPECT
AROUND HERE, NONE.

24:10.875 --> 24:12.107
YEAH?
WELL, THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

24:12.143 --> 24:13.242
NO, NO, NO.

24:13.277 --> 24:15.577
BUT ONLY ONE OF US TRIED
TO TAKE THEIR OWN LIFE.

24:15.613 --> 24:17.813
THAT'S YOUR SORRY ASS.

24:20.685 --> 24:21.817
NURSE?

24:21.852 --> 24:23.852
SO SELFISH OF YOU,
KELLY.

24:23.888 --> 24:25.354
YOU KNOW HOW MANY PEOPLE
COULD'VE USED YOUR ORGANS?

24:25.389 --> 24:27.022
HUH? BUT YOU JUST WANT TO
HANG YOURSELF

24:27.058 --> 24:29.558
AND NOT THINK ABOUT ANYBODY
ELSE, LIKE YOU ALWAYS DO.

24:29.593 --> 24:31.393
ALWAYS THINKING
ABOUT KELLY.

24:33.364 --> 24:34.964
EDDIE.

24:34.999 --> 24:36.265
BITCH-ASS RICK.

24:36.300 --> 24:38.267
TO WHAT
DO I OWE THE PLEASURE?

24:38.302 --> 24:39.335
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

24:39.370 --> 24:40.903
WHAT DO I LOOK LIKE
I'M DOING, RICK?

24:40.938 --> 24:42.738
HAVING A CONVERSATION
WITH MY FRIEND.

24:42.773 --> 24:43.973
GET OUT OF HERE, MAN.

24:44.008 --> 24:45.607
NOW.

24:45.643 --> 24:47.609
[ CHUCKLES ]
NO.

24:47.645 --> 24:49.244
NO, I DON'T THINK
I TAKE ORDERS FROM YOU.

24:49.280 --> 24:51.613
"NO, NO" NOTHING.
BOUNCE.

24:51.649 --> 24:52.982
[ LAUGHS ]

24:53.017 --> 24:55.751
RICK, LOOK AT YOU, MAN.
PROTECTING YOUR POST.

24:56.721 --> 24:58.120
ALL RIGHT,
I'LL LET YOU HAVE IT.

24:58.155 --> 25:01.523
GO RIGHT AHEAD.
YOU'LL SEE ME REAL SOON.

25:01.559 --> 25:07.663
♪♪

25:07.698 --> 25:13.469
♪♪

25:13.504 --> 25:15.938
YOU ALL RIGHT?

25:15.973 --> 25:19.208
I CAN'T STAND HIM.

25:19.243 --> 25:22.411
LET THAT GO, OKAY?

25:22.446 --> 25:25.247
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

25:25.282 --> 25:27.850
PAT CALLED ME
AND CUSSED ME OUT.

25:27.885 --> 25:32.588
SHE TOLD ME SHE KNEW THAT I TOLD
YOU TO SAY YOU HAD CHEST PAINS.

25:32.623 --> 25:34.356
I WON'T SAY ANYTHING.

25:34.392 --> 25:35.924
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

25:35.960 --> 25:37.993
SHE'S JUST A LITTLE MAD
BECAUSE SHE HAD TO DO PAPERWORK.

25:38.029 --> 25:41.597
BUT I TOLD HER I'D DO IT,
SO IT'S OKAY.

25:41.632 --> 25:44.066
HAVE YOU BEEN DRINKING?

25:44.101 --> 25:45.300
NO, THAT WAS HOURS AGO.

25:45.336 --> 25:47.903
I'M GOOD.

25:47.938 --> 25:50.072
AND I'M GONNA BE YOUR GUARD
WHILE YOU'RE HERE.

25:53.544 --> 25:56.745
CAN'T BELIEVE THEY GOT ME
OUT HERE IN THIS HALLWAY,

25:56.781 --> 25:59.281
WITH EVERYBODY PASSING BY.

25:59.316 --> 26:01.016
DON'T WORRY
ABOUT THAT, OKAY?

26:01.052 --> 26:02.051
YEAH, THAT'S EASY
FOR YOU TO SAY.

26:02.086 --> 26:05.320
YOU'RE NOT CHAINED UP.

26:05.356 --> 26:07.222
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

26:07.258 --> 26:10.692
I'M GONNA STAY WITH YOU
TONIGHT, OKAY?

26:10.728 --> 26:12.795
YOU DON'T NEED TO STAY
WITH ME TONIGHT.

26:15.199 --> 26:17.499
BUT I WANT TO.

26:17.535 --> 26:19.668
WHY?

26:22.173 --> 26:23.605
LOOK, KELLY.

26:23.641 --> 26:26.308
I GOT SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU, OKAY?

26:29.146 --> 26:33.415
I USED TO WORK SECURITY
FOR THE CHURCH SOMETIMES.

26:33.451 --> 26:35.384
SO YOU'RE ON
HIS SIDE, TOO.

26:35.419 --> 26:37.186
NO, I'M NOT.

26:37.221 --> 26:38.353
JUST LEAVE.

26:38.389 --> 26:40.189
NO, LISTEN TO ME.

26:40.224 --> 26:41.690
THERE'S SOME THINGS
THAT WENT DOWN

26:41.725 --> 26:43.392
THAT I'M GETTING INFORMATION
ON THAT CAN HELP YOU, OKAY?

26:43.427 --> 26:46.128
WHY SHOULD I TRUST YOU?

26:46.163 --> 26:48.030
WHAT ELSE
DO YOU HAVE TO LOSE?

26:48.065 --> 26:52.634
♪♪

26:52.670 --> 26:56.271
DO YOU KNOW MARGARET?

26:56.307 --> 26:57.473
WHO'S THAT?

26:57.508 --> 26:59.842
THAT CHAPLAIN LADY?

26:59.877 --> 27:01.276
OH, YEAH.
YEAH.

27:01.312 --> 27:03.212
SHE'S GOOD.

27:03.247 --> 27:07.082
SHE VISITED ME,
CALLED HERSELF PRAYING FOR ME.

27:08.786 --> 27:09.985
WELL, SHE MEANS WELL.

27:10.020 --> 27:12.621
NO, SHE DOESN'T.

27:12.656 --> 27:14.206
I THINK
SHE'S A GREAT PERSON.

27:14.241 --> 27:16.241
SHE'S NO

27:16.277 --> 27:18.844
WHY WOULDN'T
SHE BELIEVE ME?

27:18.879 --> 27:21.613
KELLY, I MEAN,
YOU'VE DONE A LOT.

27:21.649 --> 27:24.583
I MEAN, THERE'S A LOT OF STUFF
AGAINST YOU RIGHT NOW, SO.

27:26.287 --> 27:27.452
YOU KNOW WHAT?

27:27.488 --> 27:30.355
SHE ALSO TOLD ME
THAT THERE WERE OTHERS.

27:30.391 --> 27:33.225
WHAT?
YES.

27:33.260 --> 27:35.027
SHE SAID THAT.
YES.

27:35.062 --> 27:36.862
SHE ACTED LIKE SHE DIDN'T,
BUT SHE DID.

27:36.897 --> 27:39.665
ARE YOU SURE?
I KNOW WHAT I HEARD.

27:39.700 --> 27:41.366
I'M NOT DOUBTING THAT.
GOOD.

27:41.402 --> 27:43.735
DON'T.
OKAY.

27:43.771 --> 27:46.939
I'M GONNA WATCH EVERYTHING,
OKAY?

27:46.974 --> 27:49.408
THIS KELLY ISSACS?

27:49.443 --> 27:50.943
YES.
YEAH?

27:50.978 --> 27:52.845
OKAY, AND YOU ARE?

27:52.880 --> 27:55.147
I'M OFFICER CONNOR.
OKAY.

27:55.182 --> 27:59.451
WELL, WE'RE GONNA TAKE YOU DOWN
FOR SOME TESTS, OKAY?

27:59.486 --> 28:00.953
OKAY.

28:00.988 --> 28:03.222
YOU'RE OKAY.

28:03.257 --> 28:04.690
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

