HEY.

28:24.011 --> 28:26.345
HEY, NAT.
WERE YOU ASLEEP?

28:26.380 --> 28:29.715
AND IF I SAY I WAS?

28:31.252 --> 28:32.351
I'M SORRY.

28:32.386 --> 28:33.719
I'm so sorry.

28:33.754 --> 28:35.153
I'M UP.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

28:35.189 --> 28:39.491
UH, I WAS -- I WAS JUST
WONDERING, IS LUSHION HOME YET?

28:39.526 --> 28:41.793
NO.
HE'S NOT.

28:41.829 --> 28:44.029
Oh.
Okay.

28:44.064 --> 28:46.031
ESPERANZA.

