HONEY?

28:51.071 --> 28:52.638
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

28:52.673 --> 28:55.908
You and Steven.

28:55.943 --> 28:58.243
NOTHING.
I'M -- I JUST LIKE HIM, OKAY?

28:58.279 --> 29:02.648
I DON'T -- I DON'T WANT TO
SEE HIM GET HURT.

29:02.683 --> 29:03.782
ALL RIGHT.

29:03.817 --> 29:05.717
WELL, YOU KNOW EDDIE
IS GONNA ACT A FOOL

29:05.753 --> 29:07.753
EVERY CHANCE
HE GETS, RIGHT?

29:07.788 --> 29:09.521
I KNOW.
I KNOW.

29:09.556 --> 29:14.059
SO WHY DON'T YOU SHUT THIS DOWN
ONCE AND FOR ALL?

29:14.094 --> 29:16.795
HOW, NATALIE?
I'VE -- I'VE TRIED EVERYTHING!

29:16.830 --> 29:17.863
NOTHING WORKS
WITH THIS GUY.

29:17.898 --> 29:19.164
THAT'S WHO HE IS.

29:19.199 --> 29:20.799
What do you
want me to do?

29:20.834 --> 29:22.534
I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T KNOW.

29:22.569 --> 29:25.938
BUT ALL THIS MESS THAT'S GOING
ON WITH KELLY, YOU KNOW,

29:25.973 --> 29:27.773
YOU NEED
TO GET THIS UNDER CONTROL.

29:27.808 --> 29:30.742
I KNOW THAT.
I DO.

29:30.778 --> 29:33.812
LOOK, YOU SHOULD TRY
TO TALK TO HIM.

29:33.847 --> 29:35.981
TALK TO HIM?
I'VE TRIED THAT.

29:36.016 --> 29:37.382
Have you?
YEAH.

29:37.418 --> 29:39.651
I HAVE,
THOUSANDS OF TIMES.

29:39.687 --> 29:41.019
NO, ESPERANZA.

29:41.055 --> 29:44.022
I'M TALKING ABOUT SITTING HIM
DOWN AND HAVING A --

29:44.058 --> 29:46.458
a nice,
long talk with him.

29:46.493 --> 29:48.260
AND YOU THINK -- YOU THINK
THAT'S GONNA WORK,

29:48.295 --> 29:51.229
HAVING A NICE TALK
WITH HIM?

29:51.265 --> 29:52.831
HELL, NO.
Then, exactly.

29:52.866 --> 29:54.800
SO WHY ARE YOU --
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?

29:54.835 --> 29:56.301
WHY WOULD I DO
THAT AGAIN?

29:56.337 --> 29:58.937
'CAUSE WHAT ELSE YOU GOT?

29:58.973 --> 30:00.138
I -- YOU'RE RIGHT.

30:00.174 --> 30:01.673
I DON'T KNOW.

30:01.709 --> 30:04.910
TALK TO HIM,
AND TRY TO REASON WITH HIM.

30:07.214 --> 30:08.413
I'M HEARING YOU.

30:08.449 --> 30:10.615
I HEAR YOU, OKAY?

30:10.651 --> 30:12.517
ALL RIGHT, YOU BETTER.

30:12.553 --> 30:14.152
ANYWAY, I CAN'T BELIEVE
THAT YOU OF ALL PEOPLE

30:14.188 --> 30:16.989
are the one
giving me this advice.

30:17.024 --> 30:18.757
AND WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

30:18.792 --> 30:20.192
COME ON,
YOU KNOW YOU HATE HIM.

30:20.227 --> 30:22.561
STOP.

30:22.596 --> 30:24.896
LOOK, I'M JUST TRYING
TO GIVE YOU SOME OPTIONS.

30:24.932 --> 30:27.099
YOU KNOW, ALL THIS STUFF
THAT'S GOING ON WITH KELLY --

30:27.134 --> 30:29.334
I KNOW.
I KNOW.

30:29.370 --> 30:30.335
All right.

30:30.371 --> 30:32.104
WELL, JUST TRY IT.

30:32.139 --> 30:33.472
[ LOCK UNLATCHING ]

30:33.507 --> 30:34.773
YOU KNOW WHAT? WAIT A MINUTE.
LUSHION JUST WALKED IN.

30:34.808 --> 30:36.208
Hold on one second.
Hold on.

30:36.243 --> 30:37.709
OH, OKAY.

30:37.745 --> 30:40.012
HEY.
IT'S ESPERANZA ON THE PHONE.

30:40.047 --> 30:41.947
OKAY.
ESPERANZA: Hello?

30:41.982 --> 30:44.116
HEY.
HEY, LUSHION.

30:44.151 --> 30:46.284
IS -- WHAT HAPPENED?
DID YOU --

30:46.320 --> 30:48.220
WELL, UH,
STEVEN'S FINE.

30:48.255 --> 30:52.491
BUT EDDIE GOT BEAT UP
PRETTY BAD.

30:52.526 --> 30:54.426
Well, you know,
he shouldn't have got into it.

30:54.461 --> 30:56.661
BUT STEVEN --
STEVEN'S OKAY, RIGHT?

30:56.697 --> 30:57.896
Yeah.
OKAY.

30:57.931 --> 31:02.667
THANK YOU. THAT'S --
OKAY, GOOD.

31:02.703 --> 31:04.002
HEY, UH, ESPERANZA.

31:04.038 --> 31:06.004
I NEED TO
TALK TO YOU TOMORROW.

31:06.040 --> 31:08.340
OKAY, ABOUT --
ABOUT WHAT?

31:08.375 --> 31:11.410
ABOUT YOU, STEVEN, THIS.

31:11.445 --> 31:13.178
OKAY, YEAH.

31:13.213 --> 31:14.913
WE CAN.

31:14.948 --> 31:18.350
RIGHT NOW, I'M GONNA GO TAKE
A SHOWER AND GO TO BED, SO.

31:18.385 --> 31:19.918
ALL RIGHT.
WELL, UM, GOOD NIGHT.

31:19.953 --> 31:21.453
TELL NATALIE
I SAID GOOD NIGHT.

31:21.488 --> 31:24.056
GOOD NIGHT.
GOOD NIGHT.

31:24.091 --> 31:26.558
HERE YOU GO.

31:27.961 --> 31:29.127
GOOD NIGHT.

31:29.163 --> 31:31.329
GOOD NIGHT, LOVE.

31:35.586 --> 31:37.686
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

31:37.722 --> 31:41.156
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

31:41.192 --> 31:44.827
♪♪

31:44.862 --> 31:47.997
TO WHAT
DO I OWE THE SURPRISE?

31:48.032 --> 31:50.766
UH, LISTEN.
I JUST --

31:50.801 --> 31:53.268
I JUST WANT TO
TALK TO YOU.

31:53.304 --> 31:54.770
OKAY, I'M ON MY WAY.
NO!

31:54.805 --> 31:57.539
NOT -- NOT RIGHT NOW.

31:57.575 --> 31:59.942
NOT TONIGHT.
OKAY.

31:59.977 --> 32:01.543
I KNOW,
RICHARD TALKED TO ME.

32:01.579 --> 32:03.045
I KNOW
HE WANTS SOME OF THIS.

32:03.080 --> 32:05.514
ED -- ED, ED, ED, ED, STOP.
STOP.

32:05.549 --> 32:07.282
THAT'S WHAT YOU'LL BE SAYING
IN ABOUT FIVE MINUTES.

32:07.318 --> 32:08.817
CAN YOU STOP?

32:08.853 --> 32:11.086
LOOK, I'M SORE AS HELL,

32:11.122 --> 32:12.421
BUT I'LL BE ABLE
TO WORK IT OUT FOR YOU.

32:12.456 --> 32:13.622
YOU KNOW WHAT?

32:13.658 --> 32:14.923
I DON'T EVEN KNOW --
I DON'T WANT --

32:14.959 --> 32:16.659
I DON'T KNOW
WHY I BOTHER WITH YOU.

32:16.694 --> 32:17.860
OKAY.

32:17.895 --> 32:19.361
OKAY, I'M SORRY.

32:19.397 --> 32:21.797
That's better.

32:21.832 --> 32:24.033
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU,
MY DEAR?

32:24.068 --> 32:25.467
CAN YOU JUST STOP
BEING AN ASSHOLE?

32:25.503 --> 32:28.003
JUST LISTEN.
JUST STOP BEING AN ASSHOLE.

32:28.039 --> 32:30.939
WELL, THAT'S LIKE ASKING LUSHION
NOT TO BE BLACK, ISN'T IT?

32:30.975 --> 32:32.341
ED, STOP!

32:32.376 --> 32:34.677
Or Steven
not to be a dork.

32:34.712 --> 32:36.879
WELL, THAT DORK KICKED YOUR ASS,
IS WHAT I HEARD.

32:36.914 --> 32:37.880
OKAY, I SEE.

32:37.915 --> 32:39.348
SO YOU CALLED
TO RILE ME UP, HUH?

32:39.383 --> 32:41.583
NO. NO, NO, NO.
STOP. JUST LISTEN TO ME.

32:41.619 --> 32:45.087
THEN WHAT ARE WE
TALKING ABOUT?

32:45.122 --> 32:49.758
I WANT US --
I WANT US TO SIT DOWN TOMORROW

32:49.794 --> 32:52.661
AND HAVE A NICE LUNCH
TOGETHER, JUST --

32:52.697 --> 32:55.731
JUST TALK LIKE
CIVILIZED PEOPLE.

32:55.766 --> 32:57.666
HMM.
OKAY.

32:57.702 --> 32:59.935
YOU WANT TO TELL ME WHAT THIS
LITTLE LUNCH IS ABOUT?

32:59.970 --> 33:00.869
To talk.

33:00.905 --> 33:02.438
DID YOU HEAR
THE "TALK" PART?

33:02.473 --> 33:04.440
THERE'S A LOT OF THINGS
THAT WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT.

33:04.475 --> 33:07.443
I JUST --
I JUST WANT TO TALK TO YOU.

33:07.478 --> 33:08.610
YOU MISS ME,
DON'T YOU?

33:08.646 --> 33:12.548
WILL YOU JUST SIT DOWN
AND HAVE LUNCH WITH ME?

33:12.583 --> 33:14.383
SURE.

33:14.418 --> 33:15.818
OKAY.
THANK YOU.

33:15.853 --> 33:17.486
HOW 'BOUT I JUST BRING IT
OVER TO THE HOUSE AND HAVE

33:17.521 --> 33:19.822
A LITTLE PICNIC ON THE BED,
SO WE CAN GET TO IT?

33:19.957 --> 33:22.791
[ SIGHS ]

33:22.827 --> 33:25.160
HELLO?

33:25.196 --> 33:28.297
ALWAYS PLAYING HARD TO GET,
THIS BROAD.

33:28.332 --> 33:30.733
THIS IS
NEVER GONNA WORK.

33:30.768 --> 33:32.668
THIS IS
NEVER GONNA WORK.

33:34.705 --> 33:36.105
[ GROANS ]
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:36.140 --> 33:37.506
EDDIE?

33:37.541 --> 33:39.908
I SWEAR, IF YOU'VE BEEN SITTING
OUTSIDE MY HOUSE

33:39.944 --> 33:42.377
THIS ENTIRE TIME.

33:43.714 --> 33:46.215
HEY.
HEY.

33:46.250 --> 33:50.085
I JUST WANTED TO APOLOGIZE
FOR YELLING AT YOU EARLIER.

33:50.121 --> 33:51.720
ARE YOU OKAY?
YEAH.

33:51.756 --> 33:53.655
YEAH, YEAH.
I'M FINE.

33:55.593 --> 33:58.026
I'M SO SORRY THAT I GOT YOU
INVOLVED IN THIS.

33:58.062 --> 34:00.129
I FEEL --
NO, NO. DO NOT APOLOGIZE.

34:00.164 --> 34:02.264
NO, I CAN HANDLE THEM.

34:02.299 --> 34:03.499
DO YOU WANT TO COME IN?

34:03.534 --> 34:05.667
NO.
NO, I'M GONNA GO.

34:05.703 --> 34:09.938
I HONESTLY JUST WANTED TO
COME BY AND SAY I'M SORRY.

34:09.974 --> 34:12.574
IS THAT HOW
YOU GET WHEN YOU...

34:12.610 --> 34:14.610
GET MAD?
YEAH.

34:14.645 --> 34:17.412
I -- I CAN, YEAH.

34:17.448 --> 34:20.182
WELL,
THAT WAS PRETTY SCARY.

34:20.217 --> 34:21.450
I KNOW.

34:21.485 --> 34:23.485
LOOK, I'M STILL
THAT SAME LAID-BACK,

34:23.521 --> 34:26.155
SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA GUY
THAT YOU KNOW.

34:26.190 --> 34:29.191
BUT I CAN BE A MONSTER
WHEN I'M PUSHED.

34:29.226 --> 34:32.728
YOU KNOW, EDDIE WAS
THAT LAID-BACK, COOL GUY.

34:32.763 --> 34:34.963
SO, YEAH.

34:34.999 --> 34:37.232
I'M NOTHING LIKE EDDIE.

34:40.304 --> 34:45.340
DO YOU THINK THAT I WOULD DATE
A MONSTER LIKE HIM?

34:45.376 --> 34:48.343
HE BECAME THAT, OKAY?

34:48.379 --> 34:50.445
EDDIE'S AN ADDICT,
AND HE IS MENTALLY ILL.

34:50.481 --> 34:52.714
AND THOSE TWO NEVER MIX.

34:52.750 --> 34:54.316
HOW DO YOU KNOW
HE'S AN ADDICT?

34:54.351 --> 34:55.617
COME ON.

34:55.653 --> 34:58.821
THIS GUY DOES MORE BLOW
THAN THE PEOPLE WE ARREST.

34:59.824 --> 35:01.256
I MEAN, REALLY?

35:01.292 --> 35:02.324
DON'T TELL ME
YOU DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

35:02.359 --> 35:04.226
I MEAN, I KNEW
THAT HE HAD A PROBLEM,

35:04.261 --> 35:05.627
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW
IT WAS THAT BAD.

35:05.663 --> 35:07.729
NO, IT'S BAD.
IT'S REALLY BAD.

35:07.765 --> 35:10.465
LOOK,
I'M GONNA GO HOME.

35:10.501 --> 35:12.034
OKAY?

35:12.069 --> 35:13.535
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK, STEVEN.

35:13.571 --> 35:16.872
CAN -- CAN YOU JUST NOT
HOLD THIS AGAINST ME?

35:16.907 --> 35:18.140
LIKE,
ARE YOU UPSET WITH ME?

35:18.175 --> 35:19.174
NO, NO, NO.
NOT AT ALL.

35:19.210 --> 35:21.944
I AM NOT UPSET
WITH YOU AT ALL.

35:21.979 --> 35:24.413
PLEASE,
DON'T EVEN THINK THAT.

35:24.448 --> 35:27.349
BECAUSE I'VE --
I'VE BEEN HERE BEFORE.

35:27.384 --> 35:29.852
HE'S --

35:29.887 --> 35:32.254
HE'S RUINED SO MANY --

35:32.289 --> 35:33.789
I JUST -- I'VE LOST --

35:33.824 --> 35:36.258
ARE YOU TRYING TO SAY THAT
WE MIGHT BE TOGETHER, OR --?

35:36.293 --> 35:37.593
NO, I'M NOT.

35:37.628 --> 35:40.095
I'M JUST SAYING THAT
I DON'T WANT YOU TO --

35:40.130 --> 35:42.564
LOOK, WHATEVER IT IS THAT YOU'RE
SAYING, YOU'RE NOT LOSING ME.

35:42.600 --> 35:44.032
OKAY?

35:44.068 --> 35:47.102
IT'S JUST BEEN
A LONG, CRAZY NIGHT.

35:47.137 --> 35:48.370
I'M TIRED.

35:48.405 --> 35:50.472
I NEED TO GET SOME SLEEP

35:50.507 --> 35:52.741
AND GIVE THIS
SOME THOUGHT.

35:52.776 --> 35:54.443
OKAY.

35:54.478 --> 35:55.577
ALL RIGHT?
YEAH.

35:55.613 --> 35:57.713
I'M -- I'M HERE
IF YOU NEED ME.

35:57.748 --> 35:59.314
OKAY.
OKAY.

35:59.350 --> 36:01.750
WELL, ESPERANZA.
YEAH?

36:01.785 --> 36:04.219
THE MONSTER
YOU SAW EARLIER --

36:04.255 --> 36:06.121
I PROMISE I WOULD
NEVER LAY A HAND

36:06.156 --> 36:08.924
ON ANYONE
YOU CARED ABOUT, OKAY?

36:08.959 --> 36:11.827
OKAY.
OKAY.

36:11.862 --> 36:14.363
GOOD NIGHT.
GOOD NIGHT.

36:14.398 --> 36:16.331
GOOD NIGHT.

36:16.367 --> 36:18.767
♪♪

36:18.802 --> 36:20.335
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

36:21.805 --> 36:23.338
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

36:23.374 --> 36:25.407
HEY,
YOUR PHONE WAS RINGING.

36:25.442 --> 36:27.342
WHO WAS IT?

36:27.378 --> 36:28.810
I DON'T KNOW.
I PUT IT ON VIBRATE.

36:28.846 --> 36:31.179
I DIDN'T WANT TO
WAKE UP THE KIDS.

36:31.215 --> 36:33.081
OH, YEAH.

36:33.117 --> 36:34.416
OKAY.

36:34.451 --> 36:36.518
OH.

36:36.553 --> 36:38.887
IT'S RICK.

36:40.658 --> 36:41.590
RICK: Hello?

36:41.625 --> 36:43.091
HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON?
Hey.

36:43.127 --> 36:46.662
Just wanted you to know that
Kelly was moved to the hospital.

36:46.697 --> 36:47.930
WHY?

36:47.965 --> 36:49.598
Well, I told her that
if she told the infirmary

36:49.633 --> 36:51.066
that she had chest pains,

36:51.101 --> 36:52.701
it was their policy
to have her moved.

36:52.736 --> 36:54.336
So she's here.

36:54.371 --> 36:55.537
AND WHY WOULD YOU
DO THAT?

36:55.572 --> 36:57.105
To get her real help.

36:57.141 --> 36:59.708
Then we'll have her talk to
a psychologist while she's here.

37:02.246 --> 37:03.312
YEAH.

37:03.347 --> 37:04.913
UH, YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

37:04.949 --> 37:07.282
THAT'S -- THAT'S GOOD.

37:07.318 --> 37:08.917
THAT'S GOOD.

37:08.953 --> 37:10.385
So I just wanted you
to know that in case

37:10.421 --> 37:12.654
you were looking
for her tomorrow.

37:12.690 --> 37:14.089
OKAY.
THANKS.

37:14.124 --> 37:16.024
Okay.
Talk to you later.

37:16.060 --> 37:19.628
ALL RIGHT.
WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

37:19.663 --> 37:23.498
IT WAS, UH, RICK.

37:23.534 --> 37:25.300
HE HAD KELLY MOVED
TO THE HOSPITAL

37:25.336 --> 37:27.669
SO SHE COULD TALK
TO A REAL THERAPIST AND DOCTOR.

37:27.705 --> 37:29.071
THAT'S GOOD.

37:29.106 --> 37:31.006
YEAH.

37:31.041 --> 37:32.641
WHY DO YOU THINK
HE DID THAT?

37:32.676 --> 37:34.276
HMM.

37:34.311 --> 37:36.812
THINK HE'S FEELING A LITTLE
GUILTY FOR NOT HELPING HER.

37:36.847 --> 37:38.113
MM-HMM.

37:38.148 --> 37:39.648
YEAH, HE SHOULD.

37:39.683 --> 37:41.984
HEY, LOOK.
CUT HIM SOME SLACK.

37:42.019 --> 37:43.986
ALL RIGHT?
HE WAS DOING HIS JOB.

37:44.021 --> 37:47.122
YEAH.

37:47.157 --> 37:52.194
IT IS A LITTLE BIT STRANGE
THAT HE WOULD GO THAT FAR.

37:52.229 --> 37:55.497
AND WHY DO YOU THINK
THAT IS?

37:55.532 --> 37:59.334
I DON'T KNOW.
BUT I'M GONNA FIND OUT.

37:59.370 --> 38:02.738
ALL RIGHT. WELL, YOU GO ON
AND GET SOME REST.

38:02.773 --> 38:04.306
I KNOW
YOU GOT TO BE TIRED.

38:04.341 --> 38:06.208
YEAH.
YEAH, I AM.

38:06.243 --> 38:07.442
IT'S BEEN A LONG DAY.
MM-HMM.

38:07.478 --> 38:09.511
BUT WHAT ARE
YOU DOING, HUH?

38:09.546 --> 38:15.484
I AM MAKING THE KIDS' LUNCH
FOR SCHOOL TOMORROW.

38:15.519 --> 38:17.786
YOU KNOW,
I CHECKED ON THE KIDS.

38:17.821 --> 38:19.287
THEY'RE SLEEPING.

38:19.323 --> 38:20.689
YEAH, HOW'S JUSTICE?

38:20.724 --> 38:24.259
YOU KNOW,
HE IS SLEEPING JUST FINE.

38:24.294 --> 38:26.395
OH, THAT POOR CHILD.
YEP.

38:26.430 --> 38:27.629
IT'S GONNA BE FINE.

38:27.664 --> 38:29.564
IT'S GONNA BE JUST FINE.

38:29.600 --> 38:30.799
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT?

38:30.834 --> 38:32.000
YEAH.

38:32.036 --> 38:33.935
YOU DONE A LOT,
AND THAT'S ALL YOU CAN DO.

38:33.971 --> 38:35.270
YEAH, I KNOW.

38:35.305 --> 38:36.772
I'M JUST -- YOU KNOW,
I'M HURTING FOR THEM.

38:36.807 --> 38:40.142
I KNOW. I KNOW.
ME, TOO.

38:40.177 --> 38:43.311
YOU KNOW, I REALLY HOPE
SHE GETS OFF.

38:43.347 --> 38:45.580
YEAH.
ME, TOO.

38:45.616 --> 38:48.016
AND THAT LAWYER --

38:48.052 --> 38:50.452
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW.

38:50.487 --> 38:53.288
HE'S NOT GONNA REP HER.

38:53.323 --> 38:54.289
YEAH.

38:54.324 --> 38:56.858
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU KNOWN HIM?

38:56.894 --> 38:58.560
LONG ENOUGH FOR HIM
TO BE ON MY SIDE.

38:58.595 --> 39:01.363
YEAH.

39:01.398 --> 39:03.498
YEAH.
LOOK, COME ON.

39:03.534 --> 39:04.833
LET ME HELP YOU WITH THIS.
UNH-UNH.

39:04.868 --> 39:06.034
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
I GOT IT.

39:06.070 --> 39:07.469
I GOT IT.
YOU GO ON AND RELAX.

39:07.504 --> 39:09.337
I GOT THIS.
YOU SURE?

39:09.373 --> 39:11.773
YES.
ALL RIGHT.

39:11.809 --> 39:15.243
YOU KNOW, LUSHION...

39:15.279 --> 39:17.946
YOU KNOW, I WAS --
I WAS WRONG.

39:17.981 --> 39:21.049
IF WE NEED TO SPEND
THE MONEY TO HELP HER,

39:21.085 --> 39:23.452
THEN LET'S JUST DO IT.

39:23.487 --> 39:25.620
WELL, I'M WORKING
ON SOMETHING.

39:25.656 --> 39:28.790
YEAH, WELL,
I CAN'T BE THAT SELFISH.

39:28.826 --> 39:29.925
NO, NO, NO.

39:29.960 --> 39:31.126
I -- I KNOW WHERE
YOU WERE COMING FROM.

39:31.161 --> 39:32.761
IT'S JUST, YOU KNOW --
IT'S A LOT.

39:32.796 --> 39:34.563
I KNOW.

39:34.598 --> 39:36.298
BUT SHE IS OUR FRIEND.

39:36.333 --> 39:39.835
AND WE ARE GONNA DO
ALL THAT WE CAN DO.

39:39.870 --> 39:44.272
I LOVE YOU.
YOU'RE SUCH A GOOD MAN.

39:44.308 --> 39:45.974
AM I?
YOU ARE.

39:46.009 --> 39:48.076
YOU LOVE ME?
I LOVE YOU.

39:48.112 --> 39:49.811
SHOW ME
HOW MUCH YOU LOVE ME.

39:49.847 --> 39:51.780
BOY, PLEASE.
WHAT?

39:51.815 --> 39:53.615
PLEASE, I'M SO TIRED.
OH, YOU TIRED?

39:53.650 --> 39:55.183
YES, I'M SO TIRED.
OH, NO.

39:55.219 --> 39:57.085
YOU GOT TO SHOW ME
HOW MUCH YOU LOVE ME.

39:57.121 --> 39:58.820
HMM? SHOW ME.
I'M SO TIRED.

39:58.856 --> 39:59.955
PLEASE, BABY, STOP.
-WHAT?

39:59.990 --> 40:01.089
[ WOMAN SCREAMS ]
LUSHION.

40:01.125 --> 40:02.557
YOU CAN'T BE THAT TIRED.
LUSHION.

40:02.593 --> 40:04.326
WHAT?
OH, MY GOD.

40:04.361 --> 40:07.229
COME HERE!
DO YOU SEE WHAT I'M SEEING?

40:07.264 --> 40:10.665
[ WOMAN CONTINUES SCREAMING ]

